(120, 1, '2018-07-03 12:09:52', '2018-07-03 09:09:52', '[rev_slider alias="slider1"]\r\n\r\nThe shape of the emblem is round. The Central element is Association of two symbols — <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D0%B0%D0%B9%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BA_(%D0%BC%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%82)">Baiterek</a> and <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%BD%D1%8B%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BA">Shanyrak</a>. The entire space of the emblem is divided into two rings. The outer ring images the history of the great steppe. The red color symbolizes the fire. The inner ring has the symbols of independence of Kazakhstan and greatness of Astana. The color blue represents the color of <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B3_%D0%9A%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%85%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0">Kazakhstan''s flag</a>. The Emblem of Astana is approved on <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/2008">June 5, 2008</a>. Author of the concept and sketch of the new emblem is <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%B8%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%82_%D0%A0%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BF%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8_%D0%9A%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%85%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD">the President of Kazahstan</a> - <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9D%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%B5%D0%B2,_%D0%9D%D1%83%D1%80%D1%81%D1%83%D0%BB%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD_%D0%90%D0%B1%D0%B8%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%87">Nursultan Nazarbayev</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'National emblem', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'test-9-en', '', '', '2018-07-03 15:18:28', '2018-07-03 12:18:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/desc/?p=120', 0, 'post', '', 0),
